US-PRODUCT-FEED.txt.title: "Stacy Denim Boiler Suit"
US-PRODUCT-FEED.txt.description: "Jeans are the genius wear-with-anything wardrobe itemSkinny, straight, or slim, find your perfect jeans fit in the bhx denim collection. Wear with a basic tee by day and add barely-there heeled sandals to take your denim from day to night."

US-PRODUCT-FEED.txt.title: "Betty Black 3 Button Denim Hotpants"
US-PRODUCT-FEED.txt.description: "Parade your pins in a pair of shortsA versatile day-to-night option, new season shorts aren't all about showing some leg - think mid-length culottes and borrowed-from-the-boy longline styles for a more conservative take on the cropped length. But flesh-baring styles are still big for nights out, with shouty sequin shorts statement and denim hotpants easy to wear for cool-casual evenings. Dress down embellished designs with a slogan tee for added edge."

US-PRODUCT-FEED.txt.title: "Boutique Jayne Drape Front Culottes"
US-PRODUCT-FEED.txt.description: "Trousers are a more sophisticated alternative to skinniesTrousers take on a realxed silhouette for the new season, with sports tailoring setting the trends and the wide leg one to watch. US-PRODUCT-FEED.txt.title: "Boutique Kizzy Crochet Lace Skirt"
US-PRODUCT-FEED.txt.description: "Skirts are the statement separate in every wardrobe This season it's all about having fun with your hemline. Mix it up in minis, midis and maxis or go matchy-matchy and co-ordinate with a crop top. Push the boundaries in pleated pastels and fondant shade full circle styles, updating with a holographic clutch for a cool colour clash. Flirt with the skirt for your favourite every day and evening ensembles."
